Belgreen was listed on the [[1880 U.S. census]] at the time it served as Franklin County Seat. It did not appear again until 2010 when it was listed as a [[census designated place]] in the [[2010 U.S. census]].<ref>{{Cite web|first= |last= |authorlink=   |title= 2010 Census of Population - Population and Housing Unit Counts - Alabama |publisher=[[United States Census Bureau]]|date= 2010|url=https://www2.census.gov/library/publications/decennial/2010/cph-2/cph-2-2.pdf |accessdate=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220121211347/https://www2.census.gov/library/publications/decennial/2010/cph-2/cph-2-2.pdf| archive-date=January 21, 2022}}</ref>

